{"image_id": "MGM_2012_page_57", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "Customer lists. The Company recognized an intangible asset related to customer lists, which is", "bbox": [185.5, 130.0, 1094.1, 150.9]}, {"text": "amortized on an accelerated basis over its estimated useful life of five years.", "bbox": [143.8, 155.0, 840.2, 175.9]}, {"text": "Gaming promoter relationships. The Company recognized an intangible asset related to its", "bbox": [185.5, 198.8, 1094.1, 219.6]}, {"text": "relationships with gaming promoters, which is amortized on a straight-line basis over its estimated useful", "bbox": [143.8, 223.8, 1094.1, 244.7]}, {"text": "life of four years.", "bbox": [143.8, 248.8, 301.0, 269.7]}, {"text": "Deferred taxes. The Company recorded a net deferred tax liability of $381 million for the acquisition of", "bbox": [185.5, 292.6, 1094.1, 313.4]}, {"text": "the controlling financial interest in MGM China and a corresponding increase to goodwill. The net", "bbox": [143.8, 317.6, 1094.1, 338.4]}, {"text": "deferred tax liability represents the excess of the financial reporting amounts of the net assets of MGM", "bbox": [143.8, 342.6, 1094.2, 363.4]}, {"text": "China over their respective bases under Macau tax law measured at the enacted tax rates expected to apply", "bbox": [143.8, 367.6, 1094.0, 388.4]}, {"text": "to taxable income in the periods such differences are expected to be realized, net of a valuation allowance", "bbox": [143.8, 392.6, 1094.0, 413.5]}, {"text": "of $72 million. The tax-effected components of the net deferred tax liability at June 3, 2011 were as follows", "bbox": [143.8, 417.6, 1094.1, 438.5]}, {"text": "(in thousands):", "bbox": [143.8, 442.6, 279.9, 463.5]}, {"text": "Deferred tax assets- foreign", "bbox": [143.8, 480.1, 395.8, 501.0]}, {"text": "Accruals, reserves and other .......................................................................", "bbox": [164.6, 505.2, 944.1, 526.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [969.1, 505.2, 979.6, 526.0]}, {"text": "121", "bbox": [1062.9, 505.2, 1094.2, 526.0]}, {"text": "Bad debt reserve .....................................................................................", "bbox": [164.6, 530.2, 944.1, 551.0]}, {"text": "3,161", "bbox": [1047.3, 530.2, 1094.2, 551.0]}, {"text": "Long-term debt .......................................................................................", "bbox": [164.6, 555.2, 944.1, 576.0]}, {"text": "2,816", "bbox": [1047.3, 555.2, 1094.2, 576.0]}, {"text": "Net operating loss carryforward ...................................................................", "bbox": [164.6, 580.2, 944.1, 601.0]}, {"text": "58,781", "bbox": [1036.9, 580.2, 1094.2, 601.0]}, {"text": "Preopening and start-up expenses.................................................................", "bbox": [164.6, 605.2, 944.1, 626.0]}, {"text": "3,838", "bbox": [1047.3, 605.2, 1094.2, 626.0]}, {"text": "Property and equipment ............................................................................", "bbox": [164.6, 630.2, 944.1, 651.0]}, {"text": "7,822", "bbox": [1047.3, 630.2, 1094.2, 651.0]}, {"text": "76,539", "bbox": [1036.9, 663.5, 1094.2, 684.4]}, {"text": "Less: Valuation allowance .............................................................................", "bbox": [143.8, 688.5, 944.1, 709.4]}, {"text": "(71,670)", "bbox": [1028.9, 688.5, 1102.2, 709.4]}, {"text": "4,869", "bbox": [1047.3, 721.9, 1094.2, 742.7]}, {"text": "Deferred tax liabilities- foreign", "bbox": [143.8, 755.2, 425.1, 776.1]}, {"text": "Intangible assets ......................................................................................", "bbox": [164.6, 780.2, 944.1, 801.1]}, {"text": "(385,497)", "bbox": [1018.5, 780.2, 1102.2, 801.1]}, {"text": "Net deferred tax liability...............................................................................", "bbox": [143.8, 813.6, 944.1, 834.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [969.1, 813.6, 979.6, 834.4]}, {"text": "(380,628)", "bbox": [1018.5, 813.6, 1102.2, 834.4]}, {"text": "At June 3, 2011, the Company had an excess amount for financial reporting over the U.S. tax basis of", "bbox": [185.5, 868.8, 1094.2, 889.6]}, {"text": "its investment in MGM China of $3.6 billion that management does not consider to be essentially", "bbox": [143.8, 893.8, 1094.2, 914.7]}, {"text": "permanent in duration. The Company expects substantially all of this basis difference to resolve through", "bbox": [143.8, 918.8, 1094.1, 939.7]}, {"text": "repatriations of future MGM China earnings. The Company has not provided U.S. deferred taxes for the", "bbox": [143.8, 943.8, 1094.2, 964.7]}, {"text": "excess financial reporting basis expected to resolve through repatriations of future MGM China earnings", "bbox": [143.8, 968.8, 1094.2, 989.7]}, {"text": "because there would be sufficient foreign tax credits to offset all U.S. income tax that would result from the", "bbox": [143.8, 993.8, 1094.1, 1014.7]}, {"text": "future repatriation of such earnings. Deferred taxes of $5 million are provided for the basis difference not", "bbox": [143.8, 1018.9, 1094.1, 1039.7]}, {"text": "expected to resolve through repatriations of future MGM China earnings.", "bbox": [143.8, 1043.9, 817.4, 1064.7]}, {"text": "MGM China results. MGM China’s results included in the accompanying consolidated financial", "bbox": [185.5, 1087.6, 1094.1, 1108.5]}, {"text": "statements beginning as of June 3, 2011 are presented below:", "bbox": [143.8, 1112.6, 703.2, 1133.5]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31,", "bbox": [764.1, 1158.5, 999.1, 1179.3]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [710.7, 1187.7, 752.4, 1208.5]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [860.8, 1187.7, 902.4, 1208.5]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [1010.8, 1187.7, 1052.5, 1208.5]}, {"text": "(In thousands)", "bbox": [830.5, 1220.0, 932.8, 1236.6]}, {"text": "Net revenues ....................................................", "bbox": [143.8, 1241.8, 644.0, 1262.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [669.0, 1241.8, 679.4